1041
00:47:14,980 --> 00:47:17,060
 and then, God, to look at the calendar,

1042
00:47:17,060 --> 00:47:18,540
 to consider what's next, and to be like,

1043
00:47:18,540 --> 00:47:20,020
 yep, I gotta get up and I gotta go,

1044
00:47:20,020 --> 00:47:23,620
 but oh, God, won't we learn from this text?

1045
00:47:23,620 --> 00:47:26,580
 Explanation does not change us.

1046
00:47:26,580 --> 00:47:29,660
 Experience changes us.

1047
00:47:29,660 --> 00:47:32,620
 And yet, God, like Jacob, we have to be willing

1048
00:47:32,620 --> 00:47:34,740
 to take a step ourself.

1049
00:47:34,740 --> 00:47:36,860
 We need to be willing to sit longer.

1050
00:47:36,860 --> 00:47:38,700
 We need to be willing to sing louder.

1051
00:47:38,700 --> 00:47:41,500
 We need to be willing to confess bolder.

1052
00:47:41,500 --> 00:47:43,540
 We need to be able to walk forward.

1053
00:47:43,540 --> 00:47:45,940
 Need to be willing to, God, raise our hands.

1054
00:47:45,940 --> 00:47:48,620
 We need to be willing to say, I'm not leaving, God,

1055
00:47:48,620 --> 00:47:53,020
 because you're here, and where you are, oh, God,

1056
00:47:53,020 --> 00:47:55,820
 that's where I wanna be.

1057
00:47:55,820 --> 00:47:59,860
 Change us, change us, change us, change us, God.

1058
00:47:59,860 --> 00:48:03,780
 I cannot change them, but you can.

1059
00:48:03,780 --> 00:48:06,500
 And so, God, we surrender to your work now.

1060
00:48:06,500 --> 00:48:08,500
 Please, we pray in Christ's name, amen.

